{
  "stem": "14091.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "One of their sons used to come to our home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He went to school with Celia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he used to come to our home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I knew him, and Celia knew him very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We decided maybe we could get some kind of refuge there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We really came there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They let us into the house, and Piotr decided that he's going to hide us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He told the family that he's just keeping us for a day, but this wasn't true.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He made-- in the hay in the barn, he dug a hole.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he let us stay there in this whole.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And all day, we were covered with the hay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "In the night, he would come bring us some food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And this was a time then we could go out to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it went on like that for several weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At this point, I didn't know a thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I only knew when I saw my sister Chaya being killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rest of my family, at that time, I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If any survived, or if everybody was killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We stayed in that haystack for a while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he became more bold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he decided that my sister Celia, since she looked so beautiful, she was blond, she spoke perfect Polish-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that he took her into the house and told everybody of the other surrounding-- the people, that this came a cousin to stay with them for the summer.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was in the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was left in that pit of the hay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The mice had a ball with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I couldn't say anything, because people were working in this barn.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
